Depends 2

1 - Read the README
2 - Clone respository
3 - gem install bundler
4 - bundle install
5 - brew install graphviz
6 - rake db:migrate
7 - If it's after 5, go pull a pint off the keg

== Assumptions ==
You have a functioning ruby dev environment.
    it includes RVM
    and SQLite3
    and you have homebrew installed for step 5
    or know enough to make step 5 happen without homebrew
